            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1599749466311-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Chinese-style meat-free mince & green pepper stir-fry</strong> over the <strong>cooked rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chilli rounds </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
